alexandra (1.5.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Completely redesigned internal architecture of the application -- instant
    launch and new level of application performance.
  * The new database format with automatic converting for old databases.
  * Improvements to quick search and new powerful advanced search engine.
  * More information and notification area in statusbar.
  * New settings, fixes, small but comfortable features.
  * Kino-teatr.ua parser added; IMDB parser fixed.
  * German translation (by Martin Gansser).
  * Link for translators in About window.
  * Saving of playlist data on exit.

 -- Eugene Melnik <jeka7js@gmail.com>  Sun, 27 Mar 2016 16:46:02 +0300

